lead_paragraph: Fernando Alonso sought to put an end to speculation about his Formula One future on Tuesday after a positive first run in the new McLaren a year on from a heavy testing crash that left him in hospital.

headline.print_headline: Alonso Puts in the Laps and Laughs Off Rumors
